{"tid":659893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(亮劍) 印度上將：派50戰艦24小時監控印度洋","createTime":"2018-05-10T08:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T11:38:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e88c6488f8d5b2c1591e4b3d50bb349497fba70a","tid":659893,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:40:31.000Z","msg":"印度海軍總司令蘭巴（Sunil Lanba）上將近日表示，解放軍近年在印度洋的常態化活動日漸加劇，也提升了印方對中國軍隊在這片海域的擔憂，因此印度海軍將部署一支由50艘戰艦組成的艦隊，對印度洋實施24小時監控，密切關注「域外海軍力量的部署模式和周期」，重點提高海上運行能力和對印度洋的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180510/1166651.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180510%2F1166651.htm&d=PptU2tuoabB7ai56lLI6Gmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d29b7011\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180510/1166651.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ff9426634135ea4873ac52ac29eb63f2d487c6","tid":659893,"uid":124107,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c342699b2fe6ad097ecef76ad542cfe5fb3ff27a","tid":659893,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb56186d22375676724a6eb9469a2fac7fb6aa2","tid":659893,"uid":71635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:01:53.000Z","msg":"好懷疑中國成日去人地個海係咪捕緊魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db16ccc6a9281ad13b3544fb44e977ae4647030b","tid":659893,"uid":99205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:11:47.000Z","msg":"支那打鳩印度佬啦"},{"pid":"67d3c5ea2cef0dbb16dba16b4a9bbc9d544c87cd","tid":659893,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:13:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c53890a279d3fd37fa556015ac5b8878f714f32","tid":659893,"uid":1